name: Year 2022 :)
description:
This artwork was made by 11 year old NFT artist Footlong.  She has a wish that 2022 will be a great year for everyone.  She says "Everyone need a break to get rid of the stress of the past two years."

This NFT is being minted for the HEN community event "Rocking New Year JACKPOT" and will be priced/dropped/swapped when the event starts on December 28th.  

The background was painted and then the fireworks and 2022 were added via Photoshop.  Child has no Twitter for questions or comments message mentor @rblbab.

For full details about the event please go to this link.  https://twitter.com/rblbab/status/1469650566439931906
